Falls account for 8 million hospital
emergincy room visits presenting the leading
cause of visits(21,3%). Slips and falls account for over 1 million visits , or 12% of total falls.

How many Accidents happen (Do you have any stats for this) – 2018 – 
Fall on same level = 147,390 Slips without fall = 35, 330. Total injuries 182,720 injuries
What are the common injuries? – Fractures, sprains, strains, tears, bruises, contusions, concussions
